Setting Up Einstein Knowledge Creation

Check the prerequisites, turn on article creation, and map your Knowledge record fields. Then, see how agents use Knowledge Creation in the console to draft and save articles.

REQUIRED EDITIONS
Available in: Lightning Experience
Available in: Enterprise and Unlimited Editions with the Einstein for Service add-on

Before using Einstein Knowledge Creation, you must have Einstein generative AI enabled and Salesforce Knowledge enabled and set up in Lightning Experience.

To use generative AI with Einstein Knowledge Creation, first turn on Einstein Generative AI. Then, turn on Knowledge Creation.
Map Einstein Knowledge Creation Responses to Knowledge Fields
Map AI-generated responses to your Knowledge record type fields.

Give Agents Access to Einstein Knowledge Creation
Give agents access to Knowledge Creation by assigning them a permission set.
title: Setting Up Einstein Knowledge Creation in Service Cloud
